Class Indexer

  • java.lang.Object
    • indexing.Indexer
  • public class Indexer
extends java.lang.Object

      • Indexer

        public Indexer​(java.lang.String encodeMethod)
        Constructor to get our method of indexing and initialize variables.
        Parameters:
        encodeMethod - Method to use for phonetic encoding. Acceptable values are (case-insensitive): nysiis, soundex, rsoundex, dmsoundex, metaphone, and doublemetaphone. This value is set in ./config/DataMatching.properties
